It's a very good way to teach people how these historical weapons worked, how they were loaded and shot. The next step then is to get a teacher and try it with their real counterparts. Which is possible in the U.S., but -- regrettably for people outside the U.S. -- not in other countries. But after using this app, you have at least a closer idea about this part of American history.
